summary: I was commissioned to make a bunch of Pokemon desserts for the team at Framestore working on the Detective Pikachu movie!  In...
caption:
I was commissioned to make a bunch of Pokemon desserts for the team at Framestore working on the Detective Pikachu movie!

In total, I made 40+ Bulbasaur, Charmander, Squirtle, Pikachu and Jigglypuff cookies, and nearly 2 dozen Aipom tie-dye cupcakes! (My partner made the Aipom chocolates!)

This was easily the most desserts I have ever made in one go, and it was really challenging and fun! My oven was awaiting repairs for most of the week I was working on these, which was a pain to work around, but I’m so proud of the results!

summary: Pokemon Detective Pikachu (2019) The story begins when ace private eye Harry Goodman goes mysteriously missing, prompting his...
caption:
Pokemon Detective Pikachu (2019)

The story begins when ace private eye Harry Goodman goes mysteriously missing, prompting his 21-year-old son Tim (Justice Smith) to find out what happened. Aiding in the investigation is Harry’s former Pokemon partner, Detective Pikachu: a hilariously wise-cracking, adorable super-sleuth who is a puzzlement even to himself. Finding that they are uniquely equipped to communicate with one another, Tim and Pikachu join forces on a thrilling adventure to unravel the tangled mystery. Chasing clues together through the neon-lit streets of Ryme City – a sprawling, modern metropolis where humans and Pokemon live side by side in a hyper-realistic live-action world – they encounter a diverse cast of Pokemon characters and uncover a shocking plot that could destroy this peaceful co-existence and threaten the whole Pokemon universe.

Directed by:   Rob Letterman

Starring:   Justice Smith, Ryan Reynolds, Kathryn Newton, Ken Watanabe, Bill Nighy, Suki Waterhouse, Rob Delaney, Rita Ora, Karan Soni, Chris Geere

Release date:   May 10, 2019

caption:
Reality is nothing more than That 2010s Show realizing it’s in the final season and won’t be renewed.In response the showrunners decided to try making it memorable in general by taking some unexpected actions.The memories hoping to be left behind from these choices not necessarily being “good” or “bad” but more of a weird thing we’ll look back on and think a thought like this…

That actually happened.
